code: public Args startThreadPool(ExecutorService startThreadPool) {     this.startThreadPool = startThreadPool.     return this. }
public Args context(CamelContext context) {     this.context = context.     return this. }

@Override public void serve() {     if (!preServe()) {         return.     }     startExecutor.execute(() -> {         execute().         waitForShutdown().         context.getExecutorServiceManager().shutdownGraceful(getExecutorService()).         setServing(false).     }). }
